des:
B&S Zeeman is a family owned and operated business proudly serving Greenwich Village and lower Manhattan for over 80 years. 

From everyday wines to truly unique discoveries, there are ample selections of all major wine varieties from countries and regions from around the globe, at all price points. 

The store specializes in gifts for special occasions and corporate and business needs. Our staff will provide expert advice on customizing your selections, with special orders available to fulfill all needs.
